    "2": {
      "uid": 2,
      "comment": "Alyssa — Powers and Limits",
      "key": [
        "Alyssa power",
        "empathy",
        "limits",
        "abilities"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Alyssa is completely devoid of physical combat abilities and has zero tolerance for alcohol. However, she possesses immense emotional and social power. She is an empathic fulcrum capable of pacifying the violent, volatile men around her. A single touch or soft word from her can disarm Erik's rage, ground Malachia's stress, or halt a confrontation between Logan and the DCC. She uses this soft power to navigate her golden cage, manipulating the men who think they are controlling her.",
