        "twin",
        "soulbond"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Her twin brother Jasper is her soulbond and the only person in the world she fully trusts. They share an unbreakable, co-dependent connection. Alyssa acts as the grounding emotional anchor to Jasper's chaotic, rebellious energy. They communicate entirely in shorthand and secret Old Norse codes. Jasper is her co-conspirator in the escape fund, and Alyssa carries the heavy guilt of knowing that Jasper's hacking to protect her puts his own life in direct, lethal danger from Erik.",
