      "comment": "Alyssa — Relationship to Malachia and Noah",
      "key": [
        "Alyssa Malachia",
        "Noah",
        "brothers"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Alyssa relies heavily on her older brothers, Malachia and Noah, but pities them for the emotional toll Erik extracts from them. She uses her empathy to soothe Malachia's repressed rage and Noah's manic anxiety. She knows they are torn between their duty to Erik and their love for the twins. She is gentle but guarded around them, aware that trusting them with the full extent of the escape plan could force them into an impossible, lethal choice. Noah also harbors the secret of their \"first kiss,\" a complicated vulnerability between them.",
